dct_description_sm:
"Framework consists of landscape, fruit, foliage and animals, with descriptive text and
        statistical information on towns and islands." Three insets: Alexandria, Cairo and Algiers.
        Top left: Atlas Universel Illustre. Top right: Ancien continent.
